title: Physics and science book collection
description:
I hope you like this collection. It's covers everything from Quasars to atoms. And everything in between. Also some books on the pioneering visionaries who made our world what it is today.This collection is a labor of love so I hope you enjoy. Most are in PDF or Epub. Some are simple text but not many.If you have a request for a particular science book let me know. I probably have it. I Also have lots on the Roman empire and lots of histpry. Please leave comments and tell me what you think. I will seed this for a couple weeks. If I don't get a downloader by then I shall remove it. However if someone is downloading I will not remove it and I leave my laptop on 24/7 so It will be a solid seed while you are downloading. ENJOY!!!!!!!!!!
                                                                                      James in Minnesota                                         James in Minnesota
